1.title: Blossoms
1.plot: Lily is a young girl who grew up in the loving care of her parents, Camia, who is a teacher, and Dante, who is a lawyer. Because of the death threats that Dante have received related to his job, the Cruzes are prompted to relocate to Poblacion Ardiente in order to start anew. Their lives will change, however, when they come across the powerful governor of the town, Julio Ardiente.

2.title: Ligalig
2.plot: With the help of Lily and Camia, Diego tries to improve himself in the hopes that his family would appreciate him. Camia later meets Diego's father, Raul, who has hidden intentions toward her. Meanwhile, Dante discovers several unresolved cases which are connected to the Ardientes.

3.title: Lily takbo
3.plot: Dante finally confronts Emilia about what Raul did to Camia. His defiance, however, leads to a tragic conclusion. Soon, the Ardientes are out to get Camia and Lily. Will Lily abandon the life she built in Poblacion Ardiente in order to save herself and her mother?
